        "canonical_ordering_rationale": "SITE first narrows search space immediately (most impactful). FILETYPE next reduces by document type. STRUCTURAL operators (INURL/INTITLE/INTEXT) filter within content. PHRASE/TERM are search keywords. NOT exclusions applied last to remove unwanted results from the filtered set.",
        "or_sharding_behavior": "When OR operand count exceeds engine.or_max_operands, renderer can: (a) produce multiple sharded queries with batch_size=12, or (b) emit OR_TRUNCATION_RISK warning and proceed. Mode is configurable via render options.",
        "auto_quote_rules": "Multi-word values (containing spaces) are automatically double-quoted. Single words are never quoted. Phrases (PHRASE nodes) are always quoted.",
        "platform_expansion": "PLATFORM nodes expand to predefined site: operators. drive→drive.google.com, s3→s3.amazonaws.com, github→github.com, etc."
